informations (information namespace):
    - time (%H:%M:%S)
    - CPU utilization (reserve 2 digits)
    - CPU temp (average of all cores)
    - MEM used (reserve 4 digits)
    - battery (only if present, reserve 2 digits)
    - updates (only if >0, sah integration), "2+1"
    - mpd: "[Artist - Track]", `ncmpcpp --now-playing "{{%15a - }{%32t}}|{%50f}"` (reserve 50 chars?)

    example:
    0.37 0.18 0.09 [Die Apo..Reiter - Auferstehen soll in Herrlichkeit] 0+2 54%  534M 42Â°  4% 14:55:32
